More complete descriptions and explanations are in the directory:

Documentation


Primary codon usage analysis programs:

average_codon_freqs
compile_codon_counts
compile_codon_freqs
filter_codon_counts
freqs_2_dists
freqs_2_nj_tree (requires neighbor)
modal_codon_usage
modal_usage_from_counts
native_codon_usage (requires formatdb and blastall)
score_codon_counts
score_codon_freqs


Program for making a printer plot (text or html) of a tree:

sketech_tree


Perl modules used by the above programs:

bidir_best_hits.pm
gjocodonlib.pm
gjonativecodonlib.pm
gjonewicklib.pm
gjoparseblast.pm
gjophylip.pm
gjosegmentlib.pm
gjoseqlib.pm
gjostat.pm
high_expression_ref_ab.pm


Support programs in perl:

codon_freq_eval_pl
project_codon_usage_onto_axis_pl
score_codon_freqs_pl


Support programs in C:

Source code:
codon_counts_x_and_p.c
codon_freq_eval_2.c
project_codon_usage_onto_axis.c

Files included by the C programs above:
gjocodonlib.c
gjocodonlib.h

Directories of binary executables:

i386_osx_10.4
i386_osx_10.5
ppc_osx_10.4


External programs called by native_codon_usage and freqs_2_nj_tree, but are
NOT included in this distribution:

blastall (from NCBI blast distribution)
formatdb (from NCBI blast distribution)
neighbor (from Felsenstein PHYLIP distribution)
